---
---
<footer class="w-full" style="background-color: #07070D; border-top: 2px solid #d593ff; box-shadow: 0 -10px 30px rgba(155,95,224,0.15);">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 lg:gap-12 px-6 py-12 md:px-12 max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Brand & Business Info Column -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
            <span class="text-3xl font-black font-orbitron uppercase" style="color: #d593ff;">AbigBoysGame</span>
            <p class="font-body text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #acaab1;">
                De ultieme bestemming voor retro gamers. Tweedehands & Nieuw — uitvoerig getest, met passie geselecteerd.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-2 pt-2">
                <h5 class="text-[10px] font-orbitron font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#d593ff]/70">Bedrijfsgegevens</h5>
                <ul class="text-[11px] font-body space-y-1" style="color: #acaab1;">
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[14px]">store</span> A Big Boy's Game</li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[14px]">location_on</span> [Fysiek Vestigingsadres]</li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[14px]">business</span> KVK: [12345678]</li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[14px]">receipt</span> BTW: [NL123456789B01]</li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[14px]">mail</span> info@abigboysgame.com</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
                <a class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-sm transition-colors duration-300 opacity-80 hover:opacity-100" style="background-color: #25252d; color: #acaab1;" href="https://instagram.com/abigboysgame" target="_blank">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">share</span>
                </a>
                <a class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-sm transition-colors duration-300 opacity-80 hover:opacity-100" style="background-color: #25252d; color: #acaab1;" href="/contact">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">mail</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Links Column 1: Klantenservice -->
        <div>
            <h4 class="font-headline font-bold mb-6 pt-1 lg:pt-2 uppercase tracking-wider" style="color: #d593ff;">Klantenservice</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm font-body" style="color: #acaab1;">
                <li><a class="hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" href="/contact">Contact opnemen</a></li>
                <li><a class="hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" href="/verzendinformatie">Verzendinformatie</a></li>
                <li><a class="hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" href="/retourbeleid">Retourbeleid</a></li>
                <li><a class="hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" href="/garantie">Garantie & Kwaliteit</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <!-- Links Column 2: Informatie -->
        <div>
            <h4 class="font-headline font-bold mb-6 pt-1 lg:pt-2 uppercase tracking-wider" style="color: #d593ff;">Informatie</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm font-body" style="color: #acaab1;">
                <li><a class="hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" href="/voorwaarden">Algemene Voorwaarden</a></li>
                <li><a class="hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" href="/privacy">Privacybeleid</a></li>
                <li><a class="hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300 font-bold" style="color: #d593ff;" href="/weekdeals">Huidige Weekdeals</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <!-- Newsletter Column -->
        <div>
            <h4 class="font-headline font-bold mb-6 pt-1 lg:pt-2 uppercase tracking-wider" style="color: #d593ff;">Nieuwsbrief</h4>
            <p class="text-sm font-body mb-6" style="color: #acaab1;">Meld je aan voor exclusieve drops en retro nieuws.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
                <input class="px-4 py-3 text-sm outline-none transition-all" style="background: #000000; border: 1px solid rgba(72,71,77,0.3); color: #f9f5fd;" placeholder="E-mailadres" type="email"/>
                <button class="py-3 font-orbitron font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] hover:brightness-110 transition-all" style="background: #d593ff; color: #ffffff;">Inschrijven</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 py-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4" style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(155,95,224,0.1);">
        <span class="text-[11px] tracking-[0.1em]" style="color: #acaab1;">© 2026 ABigBoysGame. Alle prijzen zijn inclusief btw waar van toepassing.</span>
        <div class="flex gap-6">
            <a class="text-[11px] tracking-[0.1em] hover:text-white" style="color: #acaab1;" href="/voorwaarden">Voorwaarden</a>
            <a class="text-[11px] tracking-[0.1em] hover:text-white" style="color: #acaab1;" href="/privacy">Privacy</a>
            <a class="text-[11px] tracking-[0.1em] hover:text-white" style="color: #acaab1;" href="/retourbeleid">Retour</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>
</footer>
